We may also terminate or suspend accounts deemed inactive for an extended period.
8.3 Consequences of Termination

Upon termination, you may lose access to certain or all features of the App, including any unredeemed rewards.
Any in-game items or rewards already granted through third-party gaming accounts are subject to the respective gaming platform’s policies.
